  "title": "ITAD Sorter",
  "description": "<p><strong>Redux (Seah Yong Heng Trading Pte Ltd)</strong> seeks an ITAD Sorter/Driver for our Tuas facility at 34 Tech Park Crescent, Singapore 638100. Training provided for sorting used IT equipment; no experience needed if you are keen to learn.<br /></p><p><strong>Key Duties</strong><br /></p><ul><li>Sort, tag and classify IT assets (PCs, servers, peripherals) for reuse, recycling, or destruction.</li><li>Update daily/weekly reports to supervisor and log inventory.</li><li>Drive 14ft lorry for transport needs.</li><li>Maintain clean warehouse</li></ul><p><strong>Requirements</strong><br /><strong></strong></p><ul><li>Singapore PR or SC only.</li><li>Valid Class 4 license.</li><li>Physically fit for lifting/moving equipment.</li><li>Mon-Fri 9am-6pm, Sat 9am-2pm.</li><li>Reliable and responsible; basic English/Mandarin</li></ul><p><strong>Salary & Benefits</strong><br /><strong></strong></p><ul><li>SGD 2,000-2,400/mth.</li><li>OT pay, annual/sick leave, medical after 3 mths.</li></ul><p>Email resume details to HR. Shortlisted only.</p>",
